com.example.sulemaia.Helper

Class GraphViz

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.sulemaia.Helper.GraphViz

  • public class GraphViz
extends Object
    Purpose: GraphViz Java API
    Description:
    With this Java class you can simply call dot from your Java programs
    Example usage: 
        GraphViz gv = new GraphViz();
    gv.addln(gv.start_graph());
    gv.addln("A -> B;");
    gv.addln("A -> C;");
    gv.addln(gv.end_graph());
    System.out.println(gv.getDotSource());
    Version:
    v0.1, 2003/12/04 (December) -- first release
    Author:
    Laszlo Szathmary (jabba.laci@gmail.com), Carlos Carvajal (Modificaciones al codigo original), Alejandro Silva (Modificaciones al codigo original)
